rComments: I had her as my DGD prof for this class, and what a wonderful time we had! She is so inviting, and she really made our group feel comfortable about sharing personal experiences. Grading is not stressful and is fair with Marie-Eve. Wonderful lady and I hope our paths cross again.

Had her for my labs. So sweet and caring. Really good explanations and very clear instructions on what she's looking for. Learned so much from her despite the labs being virtual! 10/10 would recommend!
Boring class but great teacher! She knows and loves what she teaches and is really good at what she does. She's highly supportive of her students and truly believes in everyone's capacities!

the class was really boring (mandatory in my program), but Marie-eve tried to make it as interesting as possible. She is super nice and cares about her students. I highly recommend her, as her exams are fair, she knows her stuff and is makes this class a bit more enjoyable
